name: Lumbung view

review 1: Hidden gem at Tabanan area. Peace and quiet village.
review 2: I think this is the one of the most beautiful landscape in Tabanan, Bali
review 3: Very nice views of the rice fields. Also a good place to stop and rest and grab snacks at the warung
review 4: Great view, no crowds,  the ultimate balinese rice paddie experience.
review 5: Definitely not on any tourist route! Quiet, picturesque and a really lovely place to spend a few moments.
